  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为新的订单系统画一个清晰的分层架构图。我想从最外层开始，用户可以通过HTTP接口和命令行工具来访问系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP Routes",
        "CLI Commands"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，HTTP Routes和CLI Commands作为入口。那事件驱动呢？是否需要Event Handlers来处理异步消息？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Event Handlers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，加上Event Handlers。这三个都属于接口层。接下来是应用层，这里放Command Handlers处理业务命令，Query Handlers处理查询，还有Application Services协调流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Command Handlers",
        "Query Handlers",
        "Application Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在图上把这三层先框出来。接口层放HTTP Routes、CLI Commands、Event Handlers；应用层放Command Handlers、Query Handlers、Application Services。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Interface Layer",
        "Application Layer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "核心层是领域层，包含Domain Entities、Value Objects、Domain Services，还有Domain Events。基础设施层放Data Persistence、External APIs、Messaging、Logging & Metrics。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Entities",
        "Value Objects",
        "Domain Services",
        "Domain Events",
        "Data Persistence",
        "External APIs",
        "Messaging",
        "Logging & Metrics"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "四层结构：Interface、Application、Domain、Infrastructure。现在来画依赖关系。HTTP Routes调用Command Handlers？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP Routes",
        "Command Handlers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，HTTP Routes、CLI Commands、Event Handlers都会触发Commands。Command Handlers和Query Handlers都需要操作Domain Entities。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP Routes",
        "CLI Commands",
        "Event Handlers",
        "Command Handlers",
        "Query Handlers",
        "Domain Entities"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了入口到Commands的连线，以及Commands和Queries到Entities的连线。Application Services也需要访问Entities吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application Services",
        "Domain Entities"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Application Services也要操作Entities。另外Command Handlers需要持久化，所以要连到Data Persistence。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Command Handlers",
        "Data Persistence"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了。Application Services到Entities，Command Handlers到Data Persistence。External APIs呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application Services",
        "External APIs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Application Services调用External APIs与外部系统交互。Domain Events要发布到Messaging系统做异步通知。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Events",
        "Messaging"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在领域层内部的关系：Entities和Value Objects？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Entities",
        "Value Objects"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Entities包含Value Objects，同时也依赖Domain Services处理复杂业务逻辑，并且会产生Domain Events。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Entities",
        "Domain Services",
        "Domain Events"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
