      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "设置了四种颜色样式。interface填#e1f5fe边框#0277bd，application填#f3e5f5边框#7b1fa2，domain填#e8f5e8边框#388e3c，infrastructure填#fff3e0边框#f57c00。",
